  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/start-team" class="btn btn-secondary back-button">← Back to Steps</a>
      <p class="step-label">Step 2 of 9</p>
      <h1>Get FIRST Involved</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Register your team with FIRST, find your region, and understand the official FTC process.</p>

      <section class="content-section">
        <ul>
          <li>Visit <strong>firstinspires.org</strong> for official competition rules and program updates.</li>
          <li>Register your new team with FIRST and request a team number.</li>
          <li>Pay the annual FTC registration fee (usually around $500-600).</li>
          <li>Join your local FTC league and connect with regional events.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="step-actions">
        <a href="/start-team-step3" class="btn btn-primary">Next: Recruit Team Members →</a>
      </div>
